	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Re: why it took so long to catch on: an instruction set not compatible with x86 (i.e. couldn't run most existing software during that time period) sure makes this difficult.  For another example, see the PowerPC.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
